description: Jennifer Raikowski  is with  Taylor Sitts  and  26 others . Dear Sedona Pines Resort,   I am gonna miss you. I'm gonna miss all the people you introduced me too, all the memories I made with you. You taught about tourism, about the beauty of traveling, about loving all cultures, about co-workers being your family, about picking me up and pushing me farther, about knowing I'm better then a simple hourly job. You taught me that bosses can be there for you, they can push you and fight with you but they can pick you up and help you grow. You taught me that I can cry at work when it's a bad day or laugh and dance because I'm weird. You gave me 3 years I'll never forget. But you also taught me it's okay to let myself grow and try new things, and I'll be forever grateful. Thank you Sedona Activity-Center Sedona and Sedona Pines Resort crew  ❤    Hello Wyndham Resorts, I hope you're ready for me.   #sedonapines #sedonaactivitycenter #family #coworkers Dayna Harvey Bella Vita
